high_descs: Walk down the corridor in the direction of a microwave, turn left beside a diningtable and walk to its long side.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around and step to a small round potato from the left.
Cut the potato on the table with the knife.
Go back to the diningtable you picked the knife from.
Put the knife on the diningtable.
Go back to the coffeetable.
Pick up the potato slice from the round table.
Turn around, walk straight until you are passing a table on your right, then go left to face the microwave.
Put the potato slice in the microwave, heat the potato up for a while, and take the potato out.
Turn around, follow the wall on your left, go left when there is no more wall on your left and get to the distant side of a kitchen countertop beside you.
Place the potato slice on the countertop.
